---
title: "applyAllowlistedWorkflowsUpdates (WorkflowRouter)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_empty: check removes.length and adds.length
    q_check_empty --> q_revert_empty: removes.length == 0 AND adds.length == 0
    q_revert_empty --> [*]: revert EmptyList()
    q_check_empty --> q_iter_removes: at least one list non-empty
    q_iter_removes --> q_remove_wf: i < removes.length
    q_remove_wf --> q_clear_targets: workflowId = removes[i]
    q_clear_targets --> q_remove_id: _applyAllowlistedTargetsUpdates(workflowId, existingTargets, empty)
    q_remove_id --> q_emit_remove: s_allowlistedWorkflowIds.remove(workflowId)
    q_emit_remove --> q_iter_removes: emit WorkflowIdRemovedFromAllowlist(workflowId); i++
    q_iter_removes --> q_iter_adds: i >= removes.length
    q_iter_adds --> q_add_wf: i < adds.length
    q_add_wf --> q_check_zero: workflowId = adds[i].workflowId
    q_check_zero --> q_revert_zero: workflowId == bytes32(0)
    q_revert_zero --> [*]: revert InvalidZeroValue()
    q_check_zero --> q_add_id: workflowId != bytes32(0)
    q_add_id --> q_add_targets: s_allowlistedWorkflowIds.add(workflowId)
    q_add_targets --> q_iter_adds: _applyAllowlistedTargetsUpdates(workflowId, empty, adds[i].targetSelectors); i++
    q_iter_adds --> [*]: i >= adds.length

    note right of q_check_empty
        INV-001: caller must have DEFAULT_ADMIN_ROLE (onlyRole modifier)
        INV-002: removes are processed before adds (order matters for re-add)
        INV-003: removing a workflowId first clears all its targets and selectors
        INV-004: zero workflowId cannot be added
    end note
